INSERT INTO `cms_resource` VALUES ('2019112319350975585661', 'recommend', 'Avatar响应式博客模版主题，免费下载', '1', '嗯，终于还是写了响应式这次。算是满足某黄的个人私欲吧，科科。虽然是个尝鲜版，但基本上该有的功能都有了。嗯嗯，废话不多说，直接切入主题。', '<p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); text-align: center; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"><img src=\"https://www.duoguyu.com/uploads/ueditor/image/20190621/1561132050443308.jpg\" title=\"Avatar响应式博客模版主题-尝鲜版，免费下载\" alt=\"Avatar响应式博客模版主题-尝鲜版，免费下载\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 680px; width: 680px;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">嗯，终于还是写了响应式这次。算是满足某黄的个人私欲吧，科科。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">虽然是个尝鲜版，但基本上该有的功能都有了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">嗯嗯，废话不多说，直接切入主题。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">说下由来，Avatar模版主题，是5月9号新写的主题，参考了一部分现在比较流行的博客风格，依旧是走的极简风。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">主要的更新日志：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1，升级全新界面风格，调整至1100px容器宽度，优化导航栏目;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2，增加“隔三岔五”栏目，不定期更新一篇语录及配图;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3，调整文章列表布局，优化资讯内容风格;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 4，首页增加“最新留言”板块，展示最近3条留言信息，将首页“推荐资源”栏目，修改为滑动视觉效果; 优化首页友联UI等。</p><p style=\"box-si