;\"># 特殊说明：</h4><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">当前模版里提供的“文章模型”，新增了一些字段（是否为模板、压缩包上传、模版类型、CMS版本、评分等级等），这是因为我将该模型处理成具备“普通文章和产品下载”的属性，在网站栏目“杂的文（普通文章）、资源下载（产品下载）”里，可以看到这两种不同显示方式的文章详情页。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">也就是说当前模版提供的“文章模型”里，在后台新建文章内容时，会看到有个“是否为模板”的选项，它就是负责在前端文章详情页里判断是否显示为“产品下载”页面的功能。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">如果你需要使用“下载”属性的文章，请在后台的文章内容里补充下图所示的内容信息（是否为模板、压缩包上传、模版类型、CMS版本、评分等级）。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">如果仅仅是普通文章，就不要去勾选该选项。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); text-align: center; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"><img src=\"https://www.duoguyu.com/uploads/ueditor/image/20190419/1555637379750544.jpg\" title=\"「多骨鱼博客」Intro v5.2 完整版-附带演示数据，博客模版主题- YzmCMS模版主题，免费下载\" alt=\"「多骨鱼博客」Intro v5.2 完整版-附带演示数据，博客模版主题- YzmCMS模版主题，免费下载\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 680px; width: 680px;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">最后，如果在安装或使用过程中，有任何问题，请在下方留言评论，或在社区里发帖，亦可在QQ群里161208398里寻求帮助。</p><p><br/></p>', '', '', '/images/cover/1561132050443308.jpg', '1', '3', '0', '0', '0', '3', '2', '0', '1', '0', '', '1', 'markbro', '2019-11-23 19:35:10', '2019-12-20 10:20:18', '0', '');
INSERT INTO `cms_resource` VALUES ('2019112319350975585663', 'recommend', 'Avatar响应式博客模版主题，免费下载', '1', '嗯，终于还是写了响应式这次。算是满足某黄的个人私欲吧，科科。虽然是个尝鲜版，但基本上该有的功能都有了。嗯嗯，废话不多说，直接切入主题。', '<p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); text-align: center; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"><img src=\"https://www.duoguyu.com/uploads/ueditor/image/20190621/1561132050443308.jpg\" title=\"Avatar响应式博客模版主题-尝鲜版，免费下载\" alt=\"Avatar响应式博客模版主题-尝鲜版，免费下载\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 680px; width: 680px;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">嗯，终于还是写了响应式这次。算是满足某黄的个人私欲吧，科科。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">虽然是个尝鲜版，但基本上该有的功能都有了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">嗯嗯，废话不多说，直接切入主题。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">说下由来，Avatar模版主题，是5月9号新写的主题，参考了一部分现在比较流行的博客风格，依旧是走的极简风。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">主要的更新日志：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1，升级全新界面风格，调整至1100px容器宽度，优化导航栏目;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2，增加“隔三岔五”栏目，不定期更新一篇语录及配图;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3，调整文章列表布局，优化资讯内容风格;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 4，首页增加“最新留言”板块，展示最近3条留言信息，将首页“推荐资源”栏目，修改为滑动视觉效果; 优化首页友联UI等。</p><p style=\"box-si